  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adults between the ages of 40 and 75 years of age suffering from moderate to severe
             chronic pain caused by osteoarthritis.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient is already taking chronic opioids or has a history of substance abuse or has a
             substance abuse disorder.
      </textblock>
